    title: "How to Ask for an Age-Discrimination-Free Interview",
    excerpt: "Plain-English guide to your federal rights against age discrimination in hiring and how to spot, document, and respond to bias in interviews.",
    category: "government-civic",
    tags: ["age discrimination", "ADEA", "EEOC", "job interview", "seniors"],
